  "description": "高效能網頁版盤點系統，專為 USB 條碼掃描器優化。純前端運行，支援 CSV 匯入與 Excel/CSV 匯出。",
  "requestFramePermissions": []
}

import React, { useState, useRef, useEffect, useCallback } from 'react';
import { 
  Scan, 
  FileUp, 
  FileDown, 
  AlertCircle, 
  CheckCircle2, 
  Search,
  RefreshCw,
  Package,
  History,
  Trash2
} from 'lucide-react';
import { InventoryItem } from './types';
import { audioService } from './services/audioService';

const App: React.FC = () => {
  const [data, setData] = useState<InventoryItem[]>([]);
  const [lastScanned, setLastScanned] = useState<InventoryItem | null>(null);
  const [inputValue, setInputValue] = useState('');
  const [error, setError] = useState<string | null>(null);
  const [isSuccess, setIsSuccess] = useState(false);
  const inputRef = useRef<HTMLInputElement>(null);

  // 1. 自動聚焦邏輯：確保掃描器輸入始終有效
  const focusInput = useCallback(() => {
    if (inputRef.current) {
      inputRef.current.focus();
    }
  }, []);

  useEffect(() => {
    focusInput();
    const handleGlobalClick = () => focusInput();
    window.addEventListener('click', handleGlobalClick);
    return () => window.removeEventListener('click', handleGlobalClick);
  }, [focusInput]);

  // 2. CSV 解析邏輯
  const handleFileUpload = (e: React.ChangeEvent<HTMLInputElement>) => {
    const file = e.target.files?.[0];
    if (!file) return;

    const reader = new FileReader();
    reader.onload = (event) => {
      try {
        const text = event.target?.result as string;
        // 簡單的 CSV 解析（考慮到前後空白）
        const lines = text.split(/\r?\n/).filter(line => line.trim() !== '');
        if (lines.length < 1) throw new Error("檔案為空");

        const headers = lines[0].split(',').map(h => h.trim().replace(/^"|"$/g, ''));

        // 驗證必要欄位
        const required = ['條碼編號', '產品代號', '品名', '期末數量'];
        const missing = required.filter(r => !headers.includes(r));
        if (missing.length > 0) {
          throw new Error(`CSV 格式錯誤，缺少欄位: ${missing.join(', ')}`);
        }

        const mappedData: InventoryItem[] = lines.slice(1).map(line => {
          // 處理可能包含引號的 CSV 欄位
          const values = line.split(/,(?=(?:(?:[^"]*"){2})*[^"]*$)/).map(v => v.trim().replace(/^"|"$/g, ''));
          const item: any = {};
          headers.forEach((h, i) => {
            if (h === '條碼編號') item.barcode = values[i] || '';
            if (h === '產品代號') item.productCode = values[i] || '';
            if (h === '品名') item.name = values[i] || '';
            if (h === '期末數量') item.bookQty = parseFloat(values[i]) || 0;
          });
          return {
            barcode: item.barcode,
            productCode: item.productCode,
            name: item.name,
            bookQty: item.bookQty,
            actualQty: 0,
            diff: -item.bookQty
          };
        });

        setData(mappedData);
        setError(null);
        setLastScanned(null);
        audioService.playSuccess();
        alert(`成功匯入 ${mappedData.length} 筆資料`);
      } catch (err: any) {
        setError(err.message || "解析失敗");
        audioService.playError();
      }
    };
    // 預設使用 UTF-8，若為中文環境 cp950 可自行調整
    reader.readAsText(file);
    e.target.value = ''; // Reset input
  };

  // 3. 掃描處理邏輯
  const handleScan = (e: React.FormEvent) => {
    e.preventDefault();
    const code = inputValue.trim();
    if (!code) return;

    if (data.length === 0) {
      setError("請先匯入 CSV 庫存檔案");
      audioService.playError();
      setInputValue('');
      return;
    }

    // 核心搜尋：優先條碼，其次產品代號
    const index = data.findIndex(item => item.barcode === code || item.productCode === code);

    if (index !== -1) {
      const updatedData = [...data];
      const item = { ...updatedData[index] };
      item.actualQty += 1;
      item.diff = item.actualQty - item.bookQty;
      updatedData[index] = item;

      setData(updatedData);
      setLastScanned(item);
      setError(null);
      setIsSuccess(true);
      audioService.playSuccess();

      // 成功視覺反饋動畫
      setTimeout(() => setIsSuccess(false), 500);
    } else {
      setLastScanned(null);
      setError(`找不到條碼或代號: "${code}"`);
      audioService.playError();
    }

    setInputValue('');
  };

  // 4. 匯出邏輯
  const handleExport = () => {
    if (data.length === 0) return;

    const headers = ['條碼編號', '產品代號', '品名', '期末數量(ERP)', '盤點數量', '差異數'];
    const csvRows = [
      headers.join(','),
      ...data.map(item => [
        `"${item.barcode}"`,
        `"${item.productCode}"`,
        `"${item.name}"`,
        item.bookQty,
        item.actualQty,
        item.diff
      ].join(','))
    ];

    const csvContent = csvRows.join('\n');
    // 加入 BOM 讓 Excel 識別為 UTF-8
    const blob = new Blob(["\uFEFF" + csvContent], { type: 'text/csv;charset=utf-8;' });
    const url = URL.createObjectURL(blob);
    const link = document.createElement('a');
    link.href = url;
    link.download = `盤點結果_${new Date().toLocaleDateString().replace(/\//g, '-')}.csv`;
    document.body.appendChild(link);
    link.click();
    document.body.removeChild(link);
  };

  const clearAll = () => {
    if (confirm('確定要清空所有資料重新開始嗎？')) {
      setData([]);
      setLastScanned(null);
      setError(null);
    }
  };

  return (
    <div className="min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center p-4 md:p-8 space-y-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto selection:bg-blue-100">
      {/* Header Section */}
      <header className="w-full flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4 border-b border-slate-200 pb-6">
        <div className="flex items-center space-x-4">
          <div className="bg-blue-600 p-3 rounded-2xl shadow-xl shadow-blue-200">
            <Package className="text-white w-8 h-8" />
          </div>
          <div>
            <h1 className="text-3xl font-black text-slate-800 tracking-tight">Smart Inventory Pro</h1>
